Contact & Directions
Sandestin Golf and Beach Resort
is located on Northwest Florida’s Emerald Coast between Pensacola and Panama City, eight miles east of Destin. Of all the Northwest Florida resorts, Sandestin Golf and Beach Resort offers the most desirable year-round sand, surf and premier golf destination for families and groups. The 2,400-acre resort is the premier destination along the picturesque Emerald Coast and is rated as the #1 Resort in Destin.
For course information or to book a tee time, please call us at
850.267.8155
.

The Baytowne Golf Club is located on Sandestin Golf and Beach Resort, a unique and charming destination on Florida’s beautiful Emerald Coast. In 2014 and 2015,
U.S. News and World Report
proclaimed Sandestin as the “#1 Resort in Destin, Florida."
There is something for everyone at this magnificent 2,400 acre property including a variety of vacation rental accommodations, sugar white sand beaches, emerald green waters, full service beach services, golf for every level of play, a top rated tennis club, water sports, marina, fitness center, spa, biking and walking trails. Plus, enjoy the Village at Baytowne Wharf, a family-friendly and fun location with shopping, dining, endless events and live entertainment.
Make Your Reservation Today >>>
